 4588   static const mxArray *emlrt_marshallOut(const char * u)
 4589   {
 4590     const mxArray *y;
 4591     const mxArray *m1;
 4592     y = NULL;
 4593     m1 = emlrtCreateString(u);
 4594     emlrtAssign(&y, m1);
 4595     return y;
 4596   }
